  <brief_title>Preventing Myocardial Ischemia by Preconditioning in Elective Operation for Abdominal Aortic Aneurysm</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Preconditioning to Prevent Perioperative Myocardial Ischemia in Elective Operation of Abdominal Aortic Aneurysm</official_title>
